rows.label: qev092806_MSG0030

Everything we heard Kelemen say...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092806_MSG0040

rows.label: qev092806_MSG0050

rows.label: qev092806_MSG0060

rows.label: qev092806_MSG0080

rows.label: qev092806_MSG0130
